  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ITypeInfoExtractor

    public class JavaTypeInfoExtractor
extends CLikeTypeInfoExtractor
    A Java type info extractor extracts type information from Java shallow entities that are either statements, methods or attributes. Other shallow entity types don't introduce any type information in Java.
